1. Grant of Use
   This documentation is provided for internal use within the organisation and its
   authorised service management functions.

2. Restrictions
   The OAS library may not be copied, distributed, published, or disclosed to external
   parties without prior written authorisation from the owning organisation.

3. No Warranty
   The OAS library is provided "as is" for operational guidance. It complements, and does
   not replace, established ITIL and ITSM processes or platform-native controls.

4. Governance
   All usage and modification of OAS content is subject to the governance defined in
   OAS-000 (Operational Analysis Standard — Governance).

Replace [[ORGANISATION]] with the legal entity that owns this repository before release.
